715723f-a.title: Manhattan: 165th Street (West) - St. Nicholas Avenue
715723f-a.text:
West 165th Street, south side, east from St. Nicholas to Amsterdam
Aves., showing prominently in the center of this block the Roman Catholic
Church and Rectory of St. Rose of Lima. The area in the foreground is
locally known as McKenna Square.
April 6, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
